statements: SELECT * FROM predictive_modeling_data;
SELECT id, item_name, price FROM predictive_modeling_data WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT item_name, quantity FROM predictive_modeling_data WHERE risk_assessment = 'High';
SELECT * FROM predictive_modeling_data WHERE price BETWEEN 30 AND 50;
SELECT id, date FROM predictive_modeling_data ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT id, item_name, price FROM predictive_modeling_data WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM predictive_modeling_data WHERE date >= '2022-01-01' AND date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT item_name, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM predictive_modeling_data GROUP BY item_name ORDER BY total_quantity DESC;
SELECT id, item_name, risk_assessment FROM predictive_modeling_data WHERE risk_assessment = 'high' ORDER BY id;
SELECT AVG(price) AS average_price, MAX(price) AS max_price, MIN(price) AS min_price FROM predictive_modeling_data;
SELECT * FROM pricing_model;
SELECT id, pricing_estimate FROM pricing_model WHERE risk_assessment = 'High';
SELECT MAX(risk_score) AS max_risk_score FROM risk_assessment_data;
SELECT id, historical_data, pricing_estimate FROM pricing_model ORDER BY pricing_estimate DESC;
SELECT id, risk_score, assessment_date FROM risk_assessment_data WHERE customer_id = 100 AND property_id = 200;

SELECT id, historical_data FROM pricing_model WHERE risk_assessment = 'High Risk' ORDER BY historical_data
SELECT pricing_estimate, risk_assessment FROM pricing_model WHERE pricing_estimate BETWEEN 500 AND 1000 ORDER BY pricing_estimate DESC

SELECT property_id, assessment_date FROM risk_assessment_data WHERE assessment_date < '2021-12-31' ORDER BY property_id

SELECT * FROM historical_data;
SELECT date, price FROM historical_data ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT risk_score, date, price FROM historical_data WHERE risk_score > 5;
SELECT model_name, model_description FROM pricing_model WHERE model_id = 1;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM model_parameters WHERE model_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM historical_data ORDER BY date DESC, risk_score ASC;
SELECT record_id, risk_score FROM historical_data WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT h.record_id, r.assessment_date, p.model_name FROM historical_data h JOIN risk_assessment r ON h.record_id = r.record_id JOIN pricing_model p ON r.record_id = p.model_id;
SELECT p.model_name, mp.parameter_name, mp.parameter_value FROM pricing_model p JOIN model_parameters mp ON p.model_id = mp.model_id WHERE mp.parameter_value >= 0.5;
SELECT r.assessment_id, r.risk_level, h.price FROM risk_assessment r JOIN historical_data h ON r.record_id = h.record_id WHERE r.risk_level = 'High';
SELECT * FROM historical_data ORDER BY data_date DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT data_id, price FROM historical_data WHERE price > 50
SELECT customer_name, address FROM customer_data WHERE customer_age > 30
SELECT customer_id, AVG(assessment_score) AS average_score FROM risk_assessment GROUP BY customer_id
SELECT MAX(amount) AS max_amount FROM transactions
SELECT * FROM historical_data WHERE price > 1000 ORDER BY data_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT customer_name, customer_age, address FROM customer_data WHERE customer_age >= 30 ORDER BY customer_age ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT customer_name, transaction_date, amount FROM customer_data JOIN transactions ON customer_data.customer_id = transactions.customer_id WHERE amount >= 500 ORDER BY transaction_date DESC LIMIT 5
